<lb n="1"/>—ṇṭu <num value="23">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 3</num><g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation"/>Āvatu rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>p pāṇṭināṭṭu muṭikoṇṭa coḻavaḷa nāṭṭuk kiḻkkaḷakkūṟṟattu <hi rend="grantha">brahmade</hi>yam Uttamacoḻaccatuppetimaṅkalattu
<lb n="2"/>—y niṉṟaruḷiṉa karumāṇikkattāḻvā<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>kku coḻapāṇṭiyaviḷākam perāl Iṟaiyili tevatāṉamāka variyiliṭṭu van=ta nilam Iruveliyum muṉpu nāṅkaḷ kāṭṭiykuṭutta nilam
